The '''Telerath Interstellar Banking Initiative''' was the banking system on [[Telerath/Legends|Telerath]]. In [[3963 BBY]] it was bought out by both the [[Draay Trust]] and [[the Adasca BioMechanical Corporation of Arkania]]. The Draay Trust quickly sold most of its portion to Adascorp, as well.

